// .claude/plans/proto-naming-conventions.md. Conventions enforced:
//   * package proto.mesh.v1 + go_package suffix for dispatch
//   * service name = <Domain>Service, methods PascalCase verbs
//   * snake_case fields, no json_name annotations
//   * org_slug at field 1 of every request (no path params on Connect URLs)
//   * timestamps as string ISO-8601 (no google.protobuf.Timestamp)
