//     missing from Go; Go +position not on Rust; MeshRunnerInfo +pod_keys
//     not on Go but populated by web at runtime; MeshEdge +binding_status
//     alias on Rust but absent on Go)
//   - clients/web/src/stores/mesh.ts           (TS interfaces re-state both
//     legacy shapes; UI reads pod_key/status/runner_id/ticket_id directly)
//
// Tag layout reconciliation: this PR adopts the **union** of the three
// shapes — every field that any layer reads survives. Drifted aliases
// collapse to the canonical name (initiator/target on edges; pod_key on
// nodes; pod_keys on runner info). The reference is .proto SSOT going
// forward — Rust + Go must mirror its field set exactly.
//
// Auth model: standard Bearer + ResolveOrgScope across all RPCs. No
// pod-scoped auth deviation (cf. binding.proto §"Auth model").

